he upper classes only resort to these tactics when the door is opened by the opposing team. BUT, I have seem numerous teams with many players hitting the middle on every occasion given. The pitcher is at a disadvantage, only that he is the closest and has less time to react.<br>
With the new composite bats the reaction time for an infielder is not good either. This is going to be a issue for many moons to come. I think pads and head gear is OK but this is not an invite to hit the middle. If you hit the guy, at least have the class to ask if he is all right and apologize. But if the game is played in the middle, you have no choice in the matter but take what is given you.<br>
I personally try to lift and drive the ball when pitched outside. But occasionally I'll top it, the pitcher can tell you chop at a ball and drag your hands. Enough said by an old timer.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showMessageRange?topicID=378.topic&start=21&stop=22>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=378.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=378.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=378.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/baseball/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=378.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.threadControl?topicID=378.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/baseball/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=378.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=378.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to sto